Bulwark is a community platform for the Army Veterans The mission and work of the Bulwark foundation are guided by the purpose and principles contained in its founding charter. Bulwark foundation is established to work in the world's toughest places to reach the most disadvantaged people & places suffering from Lack of Support, Finances, Justice, and Etcetera. We make sure Our Mission & Vision made by the Founding Charter will be accomplished by Reaching as Many Disadvantaged as possible.
